profile.name: Justin Johnson
profile.headline: Senior Software Engineer | Driving Innovation at World Labs
profile.summary: Highly motivated and experienced software engineer with a passion for AI, machine learning, and generative art. Skilled in PyTorch, C++, Python, and JavaScript.

experience.title: Senior Software Engineer

Collaborated with cross-functional teams to drive innovation and growth at World Labs.

experience.title: Freelance Developer
description: Developed and maintained multiple open-source projects, including neural networks and computer vision applications.
Provided expert consulting services to clients in the AI and machine learning space.

experience.title: Open Source Maintainer
description: Contributed to the development of popular open-source projects, including generative art and computer vision applications.
Mentored junior developers and provided guidance on best practices for open-source software development.

experience.title: Research Assistant
